{"tid":608592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安徽恐怖情人逼停女友車　潑油放火攬住死","createTime":"2018-03-28T09:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T09:52:30.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a19daff46d3f2954ed7faff2c083901090d90771","tid":608592,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/photo/bkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180328162948\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180328%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180328162948&h=158e37ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安徽蕪湖市周三（28日）上午有民眾發現一輛滑行中的車輛突然起火，消防員到場撲滅火勢後，發現車上有兩具焦屍。當地網民指死者為一對情侶，男子事發前開車逼停女方車輛，後衝進車內向女友潑油，並以「泰山壓頂」之姿放火「攬住死」。惟當地警方事後通報，僅提及事件涉及情感糾紛，但未有證實上述說法。<br />\n<br />\n根據蕪湖市公安局對外通報，事發上午10時55分，警方接報新市口有一輛汽車起火燃燒，及後證實兩名成年人被燒死。經初步調查，證實事件是因情感糾紛引發的矛盾，公安局已組織刑偵等相關部門開展調查工作。<br />\n<br />\n而網上消息指，事發前女方駕駛的紅色越野車越野路華（內地稱路虎，Land Rover），曾與男子駕駛的白色車輛展開追逐，並發生碰撞。其後車輛的安全氣囊彈出，女子一度試圖下車躲避，但遭男子追打後，再跑回車上。男方此時取出汽油，並潑向車內引燃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/photo/bkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001_02b.jpg?20180328162948\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180328%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20180328162948&h=a174cb61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警方於車輛抬出兩具焦屍。（網上圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/photo/bkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001_04b.jpg?20180328162948\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180328%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001_04b.jpg%3F20180328162948&h=11499931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/photo/bkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001_07b.jpg?20180328162948\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180328%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001_07b.jpg%3F20180328162948&h=49573019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/bkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180328%2Fbkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001.html&d=pCGlbbMDkhoO14P0X15fktr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4e26a470\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180328/bkncn-20180328145230647-0328_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b32f73beef8636e6a6ede30d44af60cff174a4c","tid":608592,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d196095eefb3afb80dd95edfbf52ae40ab584178","tid":608592,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce82c92b4365c9f47e1c613bd3dfaca53cd1c81","tid":608592,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"有冇無碼"},{"pid":"b8b9f93f77c058602f9d317e9e308e947f9e48d9","tid":608592,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dce82c92b4365c9f47e1c613bd3dfaca53cd1c81","tid":608592,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"有冇無碼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"f4b3b89a6a9a9e12980ed1db28d5901fec247759","tid":608592,"uid":11962,"like":0